Structure on how to handle the provisioning of a user
on the device

New station powers on
↓
No saved WiFi credentials found
↓
Station enters provisioning mode
↓
Phone connects to station by BLE or temporary AP
↓
User selects home WiFi network
↓
Phone sends SSID + password to ESP32-C3
↓
ESP32-C3 saves credentials
↓
Station joins the home network
↓
Station is paired to user/account/app


├── ProvisioningService.h
├── ProvisioningService.cpp
├── WiFiService.h
├── WiFiService.cpp
├── APService.h
├── APService.cpp
└── DeviceIdentityService.h